            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#医生提醒贾玲式减肥大部分人不适合#】#贾玲腹肌# 看到贾玲在《热辣滚烫》中瘦下来的样子，小卫整个人炸裂了……[裂开]原本连打针都在折磨护士的粗壮手...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E8%B4%BE%E7%8E%B2%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F%E6%8F%90%E9%86%92%E8%B4%BE%E7%8E%B2%E5%BC%8F%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E5%A4%A7%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医生提醒贾玲式减肥大部分人不适合#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%B4%BE%E7%8E%B2%E8%85%B9%E8%82%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%B4%BE%E7%8E%B2%E8%85%B9%E8%82%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#贾玲腹肌#</span></a> 看到贾玲在《热辣滚烫》中瘦下来的样子，小卫整个人炸裂了……<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[裂开]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fc_liekai-9df295d44f.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>原本连打针都在折磨护士的粗壮手臂，现在血管饱满，肌肉线条清晰……医生表示，一年减重范围大约在60斤到80斤比较合理，但具体减重多少，和自身体重基数、身体情况有关。短期内极速减重不适合大部分普通人，可能导致营养不良、低血糖等情况。即使原本体重非常高的患者，也要考虑减肥造成的心脏负担。肥胖患者如果已经因肥胖引发其他并发症，可以在医生的科学判断下进行切胃手术。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6Yt19TA" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
