            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[干饭人]" src="https://face.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/cb/2022_Foodie_org.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%98%A5%E8%8A%82%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%83%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%98%A5%E8%8A%82%E8%81%9A%E9%A4%90%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%83%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#春节聚餐如何保护胃#</span></a>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%B3%E6%88%96%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%B4%E5%A5%8B%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%83%83%E8%83%80%E6%B0%94%23&amp;extparam=%23%E6%83%85%E7%BB%AA%E4%B8%8D%E4%BD%B3%E6%88%96%E8%BF%87%E4%BA%8E%E5%85%B4%E5%A5%8B%E5%AE%B9%E6%98%93%E8%83%83%E8%83%80%E6%B0%94%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#情绪不佳或过于兴奋容易胃胀气#</span></a> 春节期间，接二连三的聚餐经常让胃连轴转，最常出现的症状之一就是胃胀气、厌食，也就是大家所说的肚子胀。<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" data-rsshub-image="href" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>医生提醒大家，造成胃胀气不仅仅是因为吃得太多，原因可能是多方面的，可以通过一些方法来进行缓解👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视网）<a href="http://t.cn/A6Y74IW8" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> <span class="surl-text">网页链接</span></a>]]></description>
